description: This Chainlink VRF common Cooter purrs with a rating of 22, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 66, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 3 for North, Nine Lives for East, Stringalong for South, and 2 for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/90223-39722-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [66 Votes, Common]
